cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE 

This paper combines reinforcement learning with computer vision techniques to study the impact of visual priors on downstream motor tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves robotics (cs.RO) and neural networks (cs.NE), which are relevant sub-categories.
